snippet.title: Game & Watch - Popeye (wide screen) (c)1981 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: This is Nintendo's Popeye, from the Game & Watch wide screen series, running in MAME.  Emulation by Henrik Algestam.  The background artwork was provided by hydef and can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1IbSRYTfKoKDgZfJZTZdnKFSpBvCvgJZV
